    "abstract": "<jats:title>Withdrawal Statement</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>The authors have withdrawn this manuscript because substantial changes have been made to the study, including multiple additional subgroup analyses that significantly alter the scope and interpretation of the findings. Therefore, the authors intend to prepare and submit a revised version as a new manuscript. As such, they do not wish this work to be cited as a reference for the project. If you have any questions, please contact the corresponding author.</jats:p>",
